-- Sherritt to Acquire a Controlling Interest in Sulawesi Nickel
-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 2010-12-01T13:11:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/sherritt-to-acquire-a-controlling-interest-in-indonesian-nickel-project.html
Sherritt International Corp. said it
has executed an earn-in and shareholders agreement with a
subsidiary of Rio Tinto Ltd. in which Sherritt will acquire an
interest in the Sulawesi Nickel Project in Indonesia. Sherritt
will acquire a controlling 57.5 percent equity interest in the
holding company that owns the Sulawesi Project.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  